{
  "chapter": "001",
  "title": "五帝本纪",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "黄帝简介",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">少典</span>的儿子，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">公孙</span>，名叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">轩辕</span>。他生下来就有神奇的灵性,年幼时就能说话，小时候聪慧敏捷，长大后忠厚机敏，成年后通达明智。"
    },
    "1.1": {
      "title": "轩辕兴起",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">轩辕</span>的时候，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">神农氏</span>的势力衰落了。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>之间互相<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">侵犯</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻打</span>，残暴地欺压<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>，而<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">神农氏</span>无力征讨他们。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">轩辕</span>就操练<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">干戈</span>武备，用武力征讨那些不来朝贡的诸侯，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都来归附臣服。但<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蚩尤</span>最为凶暴，没有人能征讨他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">炎帝</span>想要<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">侵犯</span>欺凌<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都归附了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">轩辕</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">轩辕</span>于是修明德政，整顿军备，调和五气，播种五谷，安抚<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">万民</span>，丈量四方土地，训练<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">熊</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">罴</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">貔貅</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">貙</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">虎</span>等部族军队，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阪泉之野</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">炎帝</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">交战</span>。经过三次<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战斗</span>，才实现了自己的志向。"
    },
    "1.2": {
      "title": "涿鹿之战",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蚩尤</span>作乱，不服从帝的命令。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>就征调<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>的军队，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">涿鹿之野</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蚩尤</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">交战</span>，最终<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">擒获</span>并<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀死</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蚩尤</span>。"
    },
    "1.3": {
      "title": "黄帝称帝",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都尊奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">轩辕</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>，取代<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">神农氏</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>有不顺服的，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>就去征讨；平定后就离开，开山辟路，从未安定居住。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "疆域与治理",
      "text": "向东到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>边，登上<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">丸山</span>和<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">岱宗</span>。 向西到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">空桐</span>，登上<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鸡头</span>山。 向南到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长江</span>边，登上<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">熊</span>山、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">湘</span>山。 向北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">驱逐</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">荤粥</span>部族，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">釜山</span>会合诸侯符契，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">涿鹿之阿</span>建都。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "黄帝治国",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>迁徙往来没有固定的居所，以军队作为营地和护卫。官职名称都用\"云\"来命名，设置了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">云师</span>。设立<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左右大监</span>，监察各个邦国。万国和睦，而对<span class=\"mythical\" title=\"神话\">鬼神</span>山川<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">封禅</span>祭祀也特别多。获得<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宝鼎</span>，推算历法。举用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">风后</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">力牧</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">常先</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">大鸿</span>来治理人民。顺应<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天地</span>的规律，掌握幽明的占卜，生死的学说，存亡的道理。按时播种<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">百谷</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">草木</span>，驯养<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鸟兽</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">虫蛾</span>，广泛观察<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">日月星辰</span>水波土石<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金玉</span>，辛勤使用心力耳目，节约使用水火材物。因为有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">土德</span>的祥瑞，所以称号为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "黄帝子嗣",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>有二十五个儿子，其中得到姓氏的有十四人。"
    },
    "4.1": {
      "title": "嫘祖与二子",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>居住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">轩辕之丘</span>，娶了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西陵</span>的女子，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嫘祖</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嫘祖</span>是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>的正妃，生了两个儿子，他们的后代都曾拥有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>： - 其中一个叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">玄嚣</span>，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">青阳</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">青阳</span>降居到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江水</span>； - 另一个叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昌意</span>，降居到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">若水</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昌意</span>娶了<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">蜀山氏</span>的女子，叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昌仆</span>，生下<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高阳</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高阳</span>有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">圣德</span>。"
    },
    "4.2": {
      "title": "黄帝崩与颛顼立",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>去世，葬在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">桥山</span>。他的孙子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昌意</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高阳</span>即位，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝颛顼</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "颛顼治世",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝颛顼</span><span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">高阳</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>的孙子、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昌意</span>的儿子。他沉静深远而有谋略，通达事理而明察事务；培养人才以治理土地，顺应时序以效法上天，依据<span class=\"mythical\" title=\"神话\">鬼神</span>以制定礼义，调理五气以施行教化，诚心诚意地<span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">祭祀</span>。 - 向北到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">幽陵</span>， - 向南到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">交阯</span>， - 向西到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">流沙</span>， - 向东到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蟠木</span>。 <span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">动静</span>之物，无论大小的神灵，<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">日月</span>所照耀的地方，没有不归顺的。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "颛顼传承",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝颛顼</span>生子叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穷蝉</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">颛顼</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">玄嚣</span>的孙子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高辛</span>即位，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝喾</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "帝喾世系",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝喾</span><span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">高辛</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>的曾孙。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高辛</span>的父亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蟜极</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蟜极</span>的父亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">玄嚣</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">玄嚣</span>的父亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>。从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">玄嚣</span>到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蟜极</span>都没有在帝位，到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高辛</span>才即帝位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高辛</span>对于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">颛顼</span>来说是同族侄子。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "帝喾德政",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高辛</span>生下来就有<span class=\"mythical\" title=\"神话\">神灵</span>，自己说出自己的名字。他广泛施予恩惠，不为自己谋私利。耳聪能知道远方的事，目明能察见细微的事。顺应天道的准则，了解人民的急需。仁爱而有威严，恩惠而有信用，修养自身而<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>归服。 - 取用土地的财富却节约使用， - 抚育教导万民而施予有益的教诲， - 推算<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">日月</span>的运行而迎送它们， - 明白<span class=\"mythical\" title=\"神话\">鬼神</span>的道理而恭敬侍奉。 他的容貌庄重，他的德行高尚。他的行动合时，他的服饰端正。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝喾</span>诚挚公正而遍及<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>，<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">日月</span>所照耀、风雨所到达的地方，没有不归服的。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "帝喾传位",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝喾</span>娶了<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">陈锋氏</span>的女子，生下<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">放勋</span>。又娶了<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">娵訾氏</span>的女子，生下<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">挚</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝喾</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">挚</span>继位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝挚</span>即位后，治理不善，他的弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">放勋</span>即位，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝尧</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "帝尧仁德",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝尧</span>就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">放勋</span>。他的仁德如天一样广大，他的智慧如神一样灵妙。接近他如同太阳一样温暖，远望他如同云彩一样庄严。富有却不骄横，尊贵却不怠慢。身穿黄色的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span>服，乘坐红色的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>，驾着<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">白马</span>。能够彰明德行，使九族和睦。九族和睦后，又整顿<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>政治清明，万国和谐团结。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "制定历法",
      "text": "于是命令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">羲</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">和</span>，恭敬顺应<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">昊天</span>，用数学方法推算<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">日月星辰</span>的运行，恭敬地向人民授予农时。"
    },
    "11.1": {
      "title": "春季东方",
      "text": "分别命令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">羲仲</span>，居住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郁夷</span>，叫做<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">旸谷</span>。恭敬地观察日出，安排好春耕的农事。<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">日中</span>时刻，<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">星鸟</span>出现，用来确定<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">中春</span>。这时人民分散劳作，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鸟兽</span>繁育幼小。"
    },
    "11.2": {
      "title": "夏季南方",
      "text": "又命令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">羲叔</span>，居住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南交</span>。安排好夏季的农事，恭敬地办理。<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">日永</span>，<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">星火</span>出现，用来确定<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">中夏</span>。这时人民聚居，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鸟兽</span>羽毛稀疏。"
    },
    "11.3": {
      "title": "秋季西方",
      "text": "又命令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">和仲</span>，居住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西土</span>，叫做<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">昧谷</span>。恭敬地观察日落，安排好秋收的农事。<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">夜中</span>时刻，<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">星虚</span>出现，用来确定<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">中秋</span>。这时人民安适，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鸟兽</span>羽毛丰满。"
    },
    "11.4": {
      "title": "冬季北方",
      "text": "又命令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">和叔</span>，居住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北方</span>，叫做<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">幽都</span>。监察隐伏的事物。<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">日短</span>，<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">星昴</span>出现，用来确定<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">中冬</span>。这时人民入室取暖，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鸟兽</span>生出细毛。"
    },
    "11.5": {
      "title": "历法与考核",
      "text": "一年<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三百六十六日</span>，用<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">闰月</span>来校正<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">四时</span>。督促整顿<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">百官</span>，各种事业都兴盛起来。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "尧选继承人",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>说：\"谁能够胜任这些事务？\""
    },
    "12.1-12.3": {
      "title": "放齐举丹朱",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">放齐</span>说：\"您的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丹朱</span>通达开明。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>说：\"唉！他愚顽凶恶，不能用。\""
    },
    "12.4-12.6": {
      "title": "讙兜举共工",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>又说：\"谁可以呢？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">讙兜</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">共工</span>广泛聚集民众推行功业，可以任用。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">共工</span>善于花言巧语，实际却邪僻，表面恭敬实则傲慢欺天，不能用。\""
    },
    "12.7-12.11": {
      "title": "四岳举鲧",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>又说：\"唉，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">四岳</span>，洪水滔滔漫天，浩浩荡荡包围山陵，百姓为此忧虑，有谁能够治理？\"大家都说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲧</span>可以。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲧</span>违背命令破坏族规，不能用。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">岳</span>说：\"与其这样，不如试一试，不行再罢免。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>于是听从岳的意见任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲧</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">九年（时长）</span>过去了，治水没有成功。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "尧举舜",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>说：\"唉！<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">四岳</span>：我在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">七十载（时长）</span>了，你们谁能够接受天命，继承我的帝位？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">岳</span>回答说：\"我们德行浅陋，不配担任帝位。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>说：\"那就推举所有贵戚以及疏远隐居的人。\"众人都对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>说：\"民间有一位穷困的人，叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞舜</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>说：\"是的，我听说过他。他怎么样？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">岳</span>说：\"他是盲人的儿子。父亲愚顽，母亲多嘴，弟弟傲慢，但他能够用孝心使家庭和睦，勤勉地治理家务，没有走向邪恶。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>说：\"那我来考验他吧。\""
    },
    "13.8": {
      "title": "尧试舜",
      "text": "于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>把两个女儿嫁给他，通过对待两个女儿来观察他的德行。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>让两个女儿在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">妫汭</span>谦恭守礼，遵守妇道。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>认为很好，就让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>谨慎地推行<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五典</span>，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五典</span>都能遵从。又让他全面管理<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">百官</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">百官</span>都办事有序。让他接待四方宾客，四方宾客都恭敬有礼，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>和远方宾客都很敬重他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>进入山林川泽，遇到暴风雷雨，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>行走也不迷路。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>认为他是圣人，召见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>说：\"你谋划的事情都能成功，说的话都能实现，已经<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>了。你登上帝位吧。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>以德行不足为由谦让推辞。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">正月上日</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">文祖</span>接受天命。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">文祖</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>的太祖庙。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "舜摄政",
      "text": "于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝尧</span>年老，命令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>代理<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>的政务，以观察<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天命</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">璿玑玉衡</span>观测天象，整齐<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">七政</span>。于是祭祀<span class=\"mythical\" title=\"神话\">上帝</span>，祭祀<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六宗</span>，遥祭<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山川</span>，遍祭群神。聚集<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">五瑞</span>，选择吉日，召见<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">四岳</span>和诸位长官，颁发信物。"
    },
    "14.1": {
      "title": "巡狩四方",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">岁二月</span>，向东<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">巡狩</span>，到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">岱宗</span>，举行柴祭，依次遥祭<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山川</span>。于是召见东方的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君长</span>，统一时令月份和日期，统一音律、度量衡，修订<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五礼</span>，用五种玉器、三种帛、两种活物、一种死物作为礼物，按照<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">五器</span>的规格，完成后就返回。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五月</span>，向南<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">巡狩</span>；<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">八月</span>，向西<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">巡狩</span>；<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一月</span>，向北<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">巡狩</span>：都和第一次一样。返回后，到祖庙祢庙，用<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">特牛</span>祭祀。"
    },
    "14.2": {
      "title": "政制改革",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五年（时长）</span>一次<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">巡狩</span>，诸侯四次朝见。广泛告知政令，明确考核政绩，根据功劳赏赐<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">服</span>。设立十二个州，疏通河道。用图画展示<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">典刑</span>，流放来宽宥<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">五刑</span>，鞭打作为<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">官刑</span>，教鞭作为<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">教刑</span>，罚金作为<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">赎刑</span>。因过失造成的灾祸，予以<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦免</span>；怙恶不悛作恶的，予以<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刑罚</span>。谨慎啊，谨慎啊，只有刑罚才能使社会安定！"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "惩办四罪",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">讙兜</span>进言推举<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">共工</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>说不可以但还是试用他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">工师</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">共工</span>果然淫乱邪僻。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">四岳</span>推举<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲧</span>治理洪水，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>认为不可以，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">岳</span>强烈请求试用，试用后没有成效，所以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>不满意。<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">三苗</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江淮</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荆州</span>屡次作乱。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>回来向帝禀告，请求： - 流放<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">共工</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">幽陵</span>，以教化<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">北狄</span>； - 放逐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">驩兜</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">崇山</span>，以教化<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">南蛮</span>； - 迁徙<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">三苗</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三危</span>，以教化<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">西戎</span>； - 在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">羽山</span>诛杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲧</span>，以教化<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">东夷</span>。 处罚了四个罪人后，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>都归服了。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "尧崩舜立",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">七十年（时长）</span>遇到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十年（时长）</span>后年老，命令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>代理<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>的政务，向天推荐他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>退位共<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十八年（时长）</span>后去世。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>悲哀，如同死了父母一样。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>内，四方都不举办音乐，来怀念<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>。"
    },
    "16.1": {
      "title": "尧传位于舜",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>知道儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丹朱</span>不贤能，不足以授予<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>，于是才权宜地把帝位授给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>。授给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>，则<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>得利而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丹朱</span>受损；授给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丹朱</span>，则<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>受损而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丹朱</span>得利。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>说：\"最终不能因<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>受损而让一个人得利\"，于是就把<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>授给了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>。"
    },
    "16.2": {
      "title": "舜即帝位",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>去世，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>守丧完毕，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>让位避让到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南河之南</span>以让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丹朱</span>。但<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">朝觐</span>不去<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丹朱</span>那里而去<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>那里，诉讼的不去<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丹朱</span>那里而去<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>那里，歌颂的不歌颂<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丹朱</span>而歌颂<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>说：\"这是天意啊\"，然后才到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>登上<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>的位置，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝舜</span>。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "舜的世系",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞舜</span>，名字叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">重华</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">重华</span>的父亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">瞽叟</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">瞽叟</span>的父亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桥牛</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桥牛</span>的父亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句望</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句望</span>的父亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">敬康</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">敬康</span>的父亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穷蝉</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穷蝉</span>的父亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝颛顼</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">颛顼</span>的父亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昌意</span>：到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>已经七代了。从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穷蝉</span>到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝舜</span>，都是地位低微的平民。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "舜的家庭",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>的父亲<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">瞽叟</span>是盲人，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>的母亲去世后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">瞽叟</span>又娶妻生了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">象</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">象</span>很傲慢。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">瞽叟</span>宠爱后妻的儿子，常常想杀死<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>就逃避；等到有小过错时，就接受惩罚。顺从地侍奉父亲、后母和弟弟，一天比一天笃诚谨慎，毫不松懈。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "舜的品德",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">冀州</span>人。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">历山</span>耕作，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雷泽</span>捕鱼，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河滨</span>制陶，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">寿丘</span>制作器具，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">负夏</span>经商。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>的父亲<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">瞽叟</span>愚顽，母亲多嘴，弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">象</span>傲慢，都想杀死<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>顺从适应却不失儿子的本分，对兄弟既孝顺又慈爱。他们想杀害<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>却找不到机会；等他们找他时，他常在身边。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "舜二十岁以孝闻名",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>二十岁时就以孝顺闻名。三十岁时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝尧</span>询问可用之人，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">四岳</span>都推荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞舜</span>，说可以。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>把两个女儿嫁给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>来观察他的居家表现，派九个儿子与他相处来观察他的处事能力。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">妫汭</span>，居家行为更加谨慎。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>的两个女儿不敢因为高贵而对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>的亲戚傲慢，很有妇道。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>的九个儿子都更加淳厚。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">历山</span>耕作，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">历山</span>的人都互相让田界；在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雷泽</span>捕鱼，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雷泽</span>的人都互相让居所；在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河滨</span>制陶，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河滨</span>的器具都不粗劣。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年（时长）</span>他所居住的地方就形成聚落，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>成为城邑，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>成为都城。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>于是赏赐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>细葛布<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span>，给他<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">琴</span>，为他建造<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">仓廪</span>，赐给他<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛羊</span>。"
    },
    "20.1": {
      "title": "焚廪之难",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">瞽叟</span>还想杀死他，让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>登上粮仓涂泥，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">瞽叟</span>从下面放火焚烧粮仓。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>就用两个斗笠保护自己跳下来，离开了，得以不死。"
    },
    "20.2": {
      "title": "掘井之险",
      "text": "后来<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">瞽叟</span>又让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>挖井，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>挖井时在旁边挖了一个隐蔽的通道出口。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>进入井深处后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">瞽叟</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">象</span>一起往下倒土填井，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>从隐蔽通道出来，离开了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">瞽叟</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">象</span>很高兴，以为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>已经死了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">象</span>说：\"这主意是我出的。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">象</span>和他的父母分配财产，于是说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>娶的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>的两个女儿和<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">琴</span>，归我。<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛羊</span>和<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">仓廪</span>给父母。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">象</span>就住进<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>的宫室，弹奏他的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">琴</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>去看他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">象</span>惊愕不高兴，说：\"我正在想念<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>，心里很忧郁啊！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>说：\"是啊，你真是众多臣仆的主人啊！\""
    },
    "20.3": {
      "title": "舜复事父母",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>继续侍奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">瞽叟</span>和爱护弟弟更加谨慎。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>就让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>管理<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五典</span>和<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">百官</span>，都治理得很好。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "举八恺八元",
      "text": "从前<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">高阳氏</span>有八个才子，世代享有他们的好处，称为\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">八恺</span>\"。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">高辛氏</span>有八个才子，世代称为\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">八元</span>\"。这十六个家族，世代继承他们的美德，不辱没他们的名声。到了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>时期，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>没能举用。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>举用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">八恺</span>，让他们主管土地，来规划各种事务，没有不按时有序的。举用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">八元</span>，让他们在四方推行<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五教</span>：父亲讲义，母亲慈爱，兄长友爱，弟弟恭敬，儿子孝顺，家内平和家外成就。"
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "流四凶族",
      "text": "从前<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">帝鸿氏</span>有个不才子，掩盖正义隐藏祸害，喜欢做坏事，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>称他为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">浑沌</span>。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">少暤氏</span>有个不才子，诋毁诚信厌恶忠良，推崇丑恶的言论，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>称他为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穷奇</span>。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">颛顼氏</span>有个不才子，不可教训，不懂好话，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>称他为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">檮杌</span>。这三族世代让人忧虑。到了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>没能除去。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">缙云氏</span>有个不才子，贪吃贪喝，贪图财货贿赂，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>称他为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">饕餮</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>厌恶他，把他和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">三凶</span>相比。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>在四方接待宾客，就流放<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">四凶族</span>，迁徙到四方边远地区，来抵御妖魔鬼怪，于是四方大门开放，说明没有凶恶之人了。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "舜得天下",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>进入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大麓</span>，遇到狂风雷雨也不迷路，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>于是知道<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>足以授予<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>年老，让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>代理<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>政务，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">巡狩</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>得以举用办事<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>才让他代理政务。代理政务<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">八年（时长）</span>后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>去世。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>守丧完毕，让位给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丹朱</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>归附<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>。"
    },
    "23.1": {
      "title": "禹等贤臣",
      "text": "而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯夷</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夔</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">龙</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">倕</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭祖</span>从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>时期就都被举用，但还没有分配职务。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>来到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">文祖</span>，和<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">四岳</span>商议，开放四门，明通四方耳目，命令<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">十二牧</span>宣扬帝德，推行厚德，远离奸佞小人，于是<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蛮夷</span>都归顺服从。"
    },
    "23.2": {
      "title": "舜任命群臣",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>对<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">四岳</span>说：\"有谁能够振兴发扬<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>的事业，让他担任官职辅助政事？\"大家都说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯禹</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司空</span>，可以发扬帝的功业。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>说：\"唉，是的！<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>，你平治水土，一定要努力啊。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>拜谢叩头，谦让给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">稷</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>说：\"好，去做吧。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">弃</span>，百姓开始挨饿，你作为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>要按时播种<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">百谷</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>不亲近，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五品</span>不和顺，你担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司徒</span>，恭敬地推行<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五教</span>，要宽厚。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蛮夷</span>扰乱中原，盗贼奸邪，你担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">士</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">五刑</span>有服制，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">五服</span>三个等级；五种流放有法度，五个等级三处居所：一定要明察能取信。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>说：\"谁能管理我的工程？\"大家都说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">垂</span>可以。于是任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">垂</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">共工</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>说：\"谁能管理我的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">草木</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鸟兽</span>？\"大家都说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>可以。于是任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">朕虞</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>拜谢叩头，谦让给众臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃虎</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">熊罴</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>说：\"去吧，你们和谐共事。\"于是让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃虎</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">熊罴</span>作为辅佐。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>说：\"唉！<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">四岳</span>，有谁能主管我的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三礼</span>？\"大家都说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯夷</span>可以。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>说：\"唉！<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯夷</span>，让你担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">秩宗</span>，早晚都要恭敬，正直而纯洁。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯夷</span>谦让给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夔</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">龙</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>说：\"好。让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夔</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">典乐</span>，教育年轻子弟，要正直而温和，宽厚而严肃，刚强而不残暴，简约而不傲慢；诗歌表达思想，歌唱延长诗句，声音依附音律，音律和谐声音，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">八音</span>能够和谐，不互相侵夺次序，<span class=\"mythical\" title=\"神话\">神人</span>因此和睦。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夔</span>说：\"啊！我敲击石磬，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">百兽</span>都随着起舞。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">龙</span>，我害怕谗言假话，震惊我的民众，命令你担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">纳言</span>，早晚出入传达我的命令，一定要诚信。\""
    },
    "23.3": {
      "title": "考核与分苗",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>说：\"唉！你们<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十有二人</span>，要恭敬啊，只有按时辅助天子的事业。\"<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>一次考核功绩，三次考核后贬黜或升迁，远近各种功业都兴起。分散迁徙<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">三苗</span>。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "群臣之功",
      "text": "这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十二人</span>都成就了功业：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大理</span>，公平执法，民众各自服从得到公正；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯夷</span>主管礼仪,上下都谦让；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">垂</span>主管<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">工师</span>，各种工匠都完成任务；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>主管<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">虞</span>，山泽开发；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">弃</span>主管<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">稷</span>，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">百谷</span>按时茂盛；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>主管<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司徒</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>亲近和睦；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">龙</span>主管宾客，远方之人都来；<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">十二牧</span>巡行，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九州</span>没有敢违背的。"
    },
    "24.9": {
      "title": "禹之大功",
      "text": "只有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>的功劳最大，开辟九座山，疏通九个湖泽，疏导<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九河</span>，平定<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九州</span>，各地按照自己的职责来进贡，不失应有的规矩。方圆<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千里</span>，直到<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">荒服</span>。向南安抚<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">交阯</span>、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">北发</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">西戎</span>、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">析枝</span>、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">渠廋</span>、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">氐</span>、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">羌</span>，向北有<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">山戎</span>、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">发</span>、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">息慎</span>，向东有长、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">鸟夷</span>，四<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>之内都敬戴<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝舜</span>的功德。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>兴起九招的音乐，招致珍异之物，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">凤凰</span>来飞翔。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>彰明德行都从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞帝</span>开始。"
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "舜的一生",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>二十岁以孝顺闻名，三十岁被<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>举用，五十岁代理<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>事务，五十八岁时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>去世，六十一岁继承<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>登上帝位。登上帝位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三十九年（时长）</span>，向南<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">巡狩</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">苍梧之野</span>去世。葬在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江南九疑</span>，这就是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">零陵</span>。"
    },
    "25.1": {
      "title": "舜传禹",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>登上帝位后，载着<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>的旗帜，前去朝见父亲<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">瞽叟</span>，恭恭敬敬只谨慎小心，像儿子的本分一样。封弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">象</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">商均</span>也不贤能，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>就预先向天推荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十七年（时长）</span>后去世。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>守丧完毕，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>也谦让给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>的儿子，如同<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>谦让给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>的儿子一样。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>归附他，然后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>登上<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>的位置。"
    },
    "25.2": {
      "title": "尧舜之子待遇",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丹朱</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">商均</span>，都有封地，用来奉祀先祖。穿着他们的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">服</span>饰，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼乐</span>也按照他们的规矩。以宾客身份晋见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>不把他们当作臣子，表示不敢独专天下。"
    },
    "26": {
      "title": "五帝世系总结",
      "text": "从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>，都是同姓但用不同的国号，以彰显德行。所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>为<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">有熊</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝颛顼</span>为<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">高阳</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝喾</span>为<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">高辛</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝尧</span>为<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">陶唐</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝舜</span>为<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">有虞</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝禹</span>为<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">夏后</span>而另立氏族，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">姒氏</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>为<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">商</span>，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">子氏</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">弃</span>为<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">周</span>，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">姬氏</span>。"
    },
    "27": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：学者多称颂<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">五帝</span>，已经很久远了。然而<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">尚书</span>只记载<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>以来的事；而<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">百家</span>谈论<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>，他们的文字不够雅正，士大夫很难谈论。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>传授给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宰予</span>关于问<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">五帝</span>德行和帝王世系姓氏的内容，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">儒者</span>有的不传授。我曾经向西到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">空桐</span>，向北经过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">涿鹿</span>，向东到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>边，向南游历<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江淮</span>，那些年长的老人都各自讲述<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>所在的地方，风俗教化本来就不同，总的来说不离古文记载的大概是对的。我看<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">国语</span>，它们阐明<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">五帝</span>德行、帝王世系姓氏已经很详细了，只是没有深入考证，它们所显现的都不虚假。古书有缺失，那些散失的内容时常在其他记述中出现。不是喜好学习深入思考，内心领会其意旨，本来就很难向见识浅陋的人讲述。我综合论述排列，选择那些言辞特别雅正的，所以著录为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">本纪</span>作为全书开篇。"
    },
    "28": {
      "title": "赞文",
      "text": "帝出自<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">少典</span>，居住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">轩丘</span>。既然继承了炎帝的历史，于是擒获了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蚩尤</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高阳</span>继承帝位，沉静深远有谋略。无论大小远近，没有不怀柔归附的。至于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝喾</span>，众多圣人同享荣耀。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝挚</span>的弟弟，号称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">放勋</span>。接近他如同太阳，仰望他如同云彩。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郁夷</span>东方劳作，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">昧谷</span>西方日落。明察举用地位低微的人，玄德传扬远播。能够禅让<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>，这两位君主真贤明啊！"
    }
  }
}